      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="en-US">
        <seg>In his 360-degree field of vision, Pivo could see the security bot thrust into view behind him.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="fr-FR">
