        <seg>Elle résonna sur la surface crystalline des murs.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="en-US">
        <seg>Just as Pivo pulled the last lever to release the airlock door, blazing plasma fire engulfed him.</seg>
