    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="en-US">
        <seg>Count on it.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="fr-FR">
        <seg>Compte dessus.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="en-US">
        <seg>Pivo, you shiny?]</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="fr-FR">
        <seg>Pivo, ça va?]</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="en-US">
        <seg>[You scorched my breeding arm, puta.] Pivo shot back with clear agitation rumbling in the harmonics.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="fr-FR">
        <seg>[Tu as brulé mon bras nouricier, puta.] répliqua Pivo dans une agitation manifeste, gargouillant dans les harmoniques.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="en-US">
        <seg>[You rather I leave you to the bot next time?] Sava turned to Sarlo.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="fr-FR">
        <seg>[Tu préfères que je te laisses au bot la prochaine fois?] Sava se tourna vers Sarlo.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="en-US">
        <seg>[Sarlo, get in here and find the console you need.</seg>
