      <tuv xml:lang="fr-FR">
        <seg>La mort possèdait cet endroit.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="en-US">
        <seg>When the team reached the control station, Sava and Berk took up defensive positions in the corridor while Sarlo and Pivo went to work on the station's dormant systems.</seg>
      </tuv>
