        <seg>[Bosses plus vite.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv xml:lang="en-US">
        <seg>If these bots have heavy ordnance, we're screwed.] Sava and Berk both unloaded suppression fire down their respective stretches of corridor before the bots even made it to the corners.</seg>
